- **in terminal 2** where CoppeliaSim is launched, you should modify simulation step time to 3 ms. To this end, enter CoppeliaSim `"Simulation > Simulation settings"` menu. In the new "Simulation Settings" panel, modify `"Time Step [s]"` to 0.003, press Enter and close the panel.
